{"id":"api/forms/NumberValueAccessor","title":"NumberValueAccessor","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/forms\", \"name\": \"@angular/forms\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/forms/NumberValueAccessor\", \"name\": \"NumberValueAccessor\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/forms\">@angular/forms</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/forms/src/directives/number_value_accessor.ts#L18-L70\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"numbervalueaccessor\">NumberValueAccessor<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/NumberValueAccessor#numbervalueaccessor\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label directive\">directive</label>\n  </header>\n  \n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4agjefaa8520ltsyr35r0fxu0\">用於寫入數字值和監聽數字輸入框更改的 <code><a href=\"api/forms/ControlValueAccessor\" class=\"code-anchor\">ControlValueAccessor</a></code>。這個值訪問器由 <code><a href=\"api/forms/FormControlDirective\" class=\"code-anchor\">FormControlDirective</a></code>、<code><a href=\"api/forms/FormControlName\" class=\"code-anchor\">FormControlName</a></code> 和 <code><a href=\"api/forms/NgModel\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgModel</a></code> 指令使用。</p>\n\n  </section>\n<h2 id=\"匯出自\">匯出自<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/NumberValueAccessor#匯出自\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <a href=\"api/forms/ReactiveFormsModule\">\n      <code>ReactiveFormsModule</code>\n    </a>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <a href=\"api/forms/FormsModule\">\n      <code>FormsModule</code>\n    </a>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n  \n<section class=\"selector-list\">\n  <h2 id=\"selectors\">選擇器<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/NumberValueAccessor#selectors\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n    <li><code>input[type=number][<a href=\"api/forms/FormControlName\" class=\"code-anchor\">formControlName</a>]</code></li>\n    <li><code>input[type=number][formControl]</code></li>\n    <li><code>input[type=number][<a href=\"api/forms/NgModel\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngModel</a>]</code></li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n\n\n\n  \n  <section class=\"description\">\n    <h2 id=\"description\">說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/NumberValueAccessor#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    \n    <h3 id=\"using-a-number-input-with-a-reactive-form\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"bemjdfiuych64i9zff10d7kp1\">將數字輸入框與回應式表單一起使用。<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/NumberValueAccessor#using-a-number-input-with-a-reactive-form\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"zxkpczmpgyr79sbgzr8u73kr\">下面的範例示範了如何將數字輸入框與回應式表單一起使用。</p>\n<code-example language=\"ts\">\nconst totalCountControl = new <a href=\"api/forms/FormControl\" class=\"code-anchor\">FormControl</a>();\n</code-example>\n<code-example>\n&lt;input type=\"number\" [formControl]=\"totalCountControl\"&gt;\n</code-example>\n\n  </section>\n\n\n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/forms\n - api/forms/ControlValueAccessor\n - api/forms/FormsModule\n - api/forms/ReactiveFormsModule\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/forms\n - api/forms/ControlValueAccessor\n - api/forms/FormControl\n - api/forms/FormControlDirective\n - api/forms/FormControlName\n - api/forms/FormsModule\n - api/forms/NgModel\n - api/forms/NumberValueAccessor#description\n - api/forms/NumberValueAccessor#numbervalueaccessor\n - api/forms/NumberValueAccessor#selectors\n - api/forms/NumberValueAccessor#using-a-number-input-with-a-reactive-form\n - api/forms/NumberValueAccessor#匯出自\n - api/forms/ReactiveFormsModule\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/forms/src/directives/number_value_accessor.ts#L18-L70\n-->"}